---
// Presence Section - Smice est présent
---

<section class="presence-section" id="presence">
  <div class="presence-container">
    <div class="presence-content">
      <div class="presence-text">
        <p class="presence-tagline">Partout où vos clients vivent leur expérience,</p>
        <h2 class="presence-title">
          <span class="highlight-blue">Smice</span> est présent.
        </h2>
        <p class="presence-description">
          Grâce à notre communauté de smiceurs, nous pouvons déployer vos <span class="highlight-bold">programmes qualité</span> rapidement et efficacement, quel que soit le secteur ou la localisation.
        </p>
        <a href="/secteurs" class="presence-btn">En savoir plus</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mspa-section">
        <div class="mspa-logo">
          <img src="/images/homepage/mspa.png" alt="MSPA - Mystery Shopping Providers Association" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="mspa-title">Membre MSPA, en France et à l'international</h3>
        <p class="mspa-description">
          Un réseau certifié, une méthodologie reconnue, une présence partout où vous en avez besoin.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="presence-map">
      <img src="/images/homepage/map.png" alt="Carte de présence Smice en Europe" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .presence-section {
    background-color: #F4F7FF;
    padding: 0 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .presence-container {
    max-width: 1224px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  .presence-content {
    margin: 60px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .presence-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .presence-tagline {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #504C54;
    margin: 0;
    }

  .presence-title {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: 'Inter', 'Inter ExtraBold', Arial, sans-serif;
 
  }

  .presence-title .highlight-blue {
    color: #6989D4;
  }

  .presence-title {
    color: #435888;
  }

  .presence-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #504C54;
  }

  .presence-description .highlight-bold {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #6989D4;
    font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  .presence-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: #6989D4;
    color: #FFFFFE;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    width: fit-content;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .presence-btn:hover {
    background: #5678c3;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(105, 137, 212, 0.2);
  }

  /* MSPA Section */
  .mspa-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
 
  }

  .mspa-logo {
    width: 80px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .mspa-logo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .mspa-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4A5FC1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mspa-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4B5563;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 450px;
  }

  /* Map */
  .presence-map {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .presence-map img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 550px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  /* ===== Tablet Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .presence-section {
      padding: 60px 24px;
    }

    .presence-container {
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .presence-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .presence-tagline {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .presence-description {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .presence-map img {
      max-width: 450px;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Mobile Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .presence-section {
      padding: 50px 20px;
    }

    .presence-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .presence-content {
      gap: 40px;
      order: 1;
    }

    .presence-map {
      order: 2;
    }

    .presence-title {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .presence-tagline {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .presence-description {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .presence-btn {
      padding: 12px 28px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .mspa-title {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .mspa-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .presence-map img {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Small Mobile ===== */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .presence-title {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .presence-tagline {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .mspa-logo {
      width: 70px;
    }
  }
</style>
